info.description:
Run XShip activity download use cases. The agent calls POST /run with { useCase, params }; the Lambda maps each use case to its backend REST endpoint:
- xshipDownloadActivityAba: GET /xshipdownload/activity/detail/{requestId}
- xshipDownloadActivityAbaRollup: GET /xshipdownload/activity/detail/{requestId}
- xshipDownloadActivityZone: GET /xshipdownload/activity/zone/{criteria}
- xshipDownloadCriteriaPeriod: GET /xshipdownload/activity/criteria/{criteria}
